BC-MENTAL-HEALTH-ELIMINATE-HNS 
  
 Monday, Dec. 13, 1999 

     Editors:     

   MENTAL-HEALTH (Washington) will not move tonight on the Hearst
News Service wire.

   Hearst News Service\Washington.
